msgstr "禁用不透明度參數的感測器。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/opacity_and_flow.rst:41
msgid "Set the maximum value on flow to 0.5."
msgstr "設定流量的最大值為 0.5。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/opacity_and_flow.rst:42
