msgstr "將不透明度視為與流量相同。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/opacity_and_flow.rst:54
msgid "Wash"
msgstr "沖刷"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/opacity_and_flow.rst:54
msgid "Will treat opacity as stroke transparency instead of dab-transparency."
msgstr "將不透明度視為筆畫透明度而不是印跡透明度。"

